## Security Notice

This lab exercise is intended for educational purposes only. The following permission change is being performed in a controlled, isolated lab environment. Do not apply these settings to production systems.

## Command Execution

```bash
sudo chmod 777 /etc
```

**Current /etc directory permissions before change:**
```
drwxr-xr-x  root root  4096 Oct 15 10:30 /etc
```

**Permissions after change:**
```
drwxrwxrwx  root root  4096 Oct 15 10:31 /etc
```

